  "reference_number": "RUS2342",
  "remarks": "\nIMO 9290309 (“THEA”) is involved in activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine or to obtain a benefit from or support the Government of Russia. Namely, THEA is involved in carrying oil or oil products that originated in Russia from Russia to a third country. \n",
